  <brief_title>Topical Analgesic Versus Saline Mouth Rinses in Post Extraction Healing</brief_title>
  <official_title>Comparison of Topical Analgesic With Saline Rinses in Post Extraction Healing Among Hypertensive and Non-Hypertensive Patients</official_title>
